    "Actually, it is needed to avoid the third-party trusted center because this mechanism is enough to ensure the verification of the public/private key.",
    "Input:User Data & Patient Medical Data Using SDP (Pid, Did, Sid,......;) Output:Allow Blockchain to input data & allow to initiate data access operations by ensuring privacy and security; 1 while (session_key == True) do 2 SDP_Information = Decrypt (SDP, BCN, session_key); 3 if (SDP_Infomation == Authenticate) then 4 node_status = getAgentNodeModule (Pid, Did, Sid) sharpen filters; 5 if (node_status == DMM) then 6 i.e.",
    "Data Management Module [patient data selection]; 7 data_status = getDataCategory (patient's medical data); 8 if (data_status == Uneventful) then 9 Temporary save data in the DMM module and need authentication to save/store data in the blockchain cloud; 10 else 11 i.e data_status are normal or eventful; 12 setPermission(True, Pid, Did); 13 i.e give permission to allow patient data(Pid) to specific(Did); 14 end 15 end 16 else if (node_status == MMM) then 17 i.e Miner Management Module [miner selection]; 18 nodeList = getAvailabeNodes (from Private Blockchain); 19 if (\"half node\" present in nodeList) then 20 Set permission to healthcare professionals that are interested to conduct patient's medical data; 21 end 22 if (\"general node\" present in nodeList) then 23 Save data into blockchain cloud broadcast blocks for verification or validation; 24 end 25 miner_status = getAvailableMiner (nodeList); 26 if (miner_status == NULL) then 27 Mine to store Uneventful data into Blockchain cloud; 28 else 29 Miner nodes add patients' medical data to the blockchain and broadcast the transaction; 30 end 31 end 32 else if (node_status == SMM) then 33 i.e Security Service Module Check vulnerability and network security threats of the different communication channels like BSN to SDP, SDP to PCA and PCA to BSN; 34 end 35 else 36 Set session_key = False 37 end 38 end Algorithm 1: Proposed Algorithm of Patient Centric Agent.",
